          <div class="scope-name">Mason Work</div>
          <div class="scope-desc">No structural changes carried out. Scope covers wall niche construction, floor concrete, floor screed preparation, vanity top construction, and wall plastering.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="scope-card">
          <div class="scope-icon">üöø</div>
          <div class="scope-name">Plumbing</div>
          <div class="scope-desc">Complete supply and drain rough-in ‚Äî hot and cold supply lines, waste pipes, and all rough plumbing for shower, basin, and WC.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="scope-card">
          <div class="scope-icon">üíß</div>
          <div class="scope-name">Waterproofing</div>
          <div class="scope-desc">Full membrane application across floor, walls to splash height, and shower recess. Critical in Sri Lanka's humid climate.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="scope-card">
          <div class="scope-icon">‚ö°</div>
          <div class="scope-name">Electrical</div>
          <div class="scope-desc">Lighting rough-in, exhaust fan wiring, and shaving/mirror point installation ‚Äî all to code and safely inside the waterproofed envelope.</div>
