          <div class="scope-icon">üî≤</div>
          <div class="scope-name">Tiling</div>
          <div class="scope-desc">Floor tiling, full wall tiling to ceiling, shower recess, and all wet areas ‚Äî using tile leveling system throughout for a perfect finish.</div>
