          <div class="scope-icon">üè†</div>
          <div class="scope-name">Ceiling</div>
          <div class="scope-desc">Waterproof PVC or gypsum ceiling installed and finished ‚Äî appropriate for bathroom humidity and fully compatible with exhaust fitting.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="scope-card">
          <div class="scope-icon">üö™</div>
          <div class="scope-name">Fixtures &amp; Shower Cubicle</div>
          <div class="scope-desc">All client-supplied fittings installed ‚Äî shower cubicle, basin, WC, mirror, towel rails, and accessories fitted and commissioned.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="scope-card">
          <div class="scope-icon">ü™µ</div>
          <div class="scope-name">Vanity Cupboard</div>
